---
import MyImage from "../../assets/me/Sanjeewa-web-developer-wordpress-&-static.avif";
---

<section id="about" class="about">
  <div class="container about-grid">
    
    <!-- My Image Section -->
    <div class="about-image-wrapper">
      <img src={MyImage.src} alt="Sanjeewa - Web Architect" class="about-image" loading="lazy" />
      <div class="image-overlay"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- About me Content section -->
    <div class="about-content">
      <span class="label">The Operator</span>
      <h2 class="headline">Code is a commodity.<br>Performance is an asset.</h2>
      
      <div class="text-block">
        <p>
          Most developers are satisfied if the code compiles. I am only satisfied if the business grows. 
          I operate at the intersection of <strong>Software Engineering</strong> and <strong>Revenue Strategy</strong>.
        </p>
        <p>
          I do not build "brochure websites" that sit idle. I architect digital ecosystems designed to 
          capture foreign markets (US/EU/UK). My systems are built on three non-negotiable pillars: 
          <strong>Speed, Security, and Scalability</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Bullet Points -->
      <div class="arsenal">
        <h3 class="arsenal-title">Technical Arsenal</h3>
        <ul class="arsenal-list">
          <li class="tech-item">WordPress Development</li>
          <li class="tech-item">High-Speed Static Sites</li>
          <li class="tech-item">Advanced SEO (JSON-LD)</li>
          <li class="tech-item">Astro & Next.js</li>
          <li class="tech-item">Headless CMS</li>
          <li class="tech-item">Core Web Vitals</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>